tics, the album received an average score of 66, which indicates \"generally favorable reviews\", based on 4 reviews.<ref name=\"metacritic1\"/>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| total_length = 42:06\n\n| title1 = The Medicine Show\n| length1 = 2:27 \n\n| title2 = Wild and Lonely\n| length2 = 4:32\n\n| title3 = Shaking\n| length3 = 3:05\n\n| title4 = Woman Like You\n| length4 = 4:32\n\n| title5 = Faded by Design\n| length5 = 3:37\n\n| title6 = I Know You\n| length6 = 4:44\n\n| title7 = This Human Chain\n| length7 = 3:51\n\n| title8 = Love Will Live\n| length8 = 4:09\n\n| title9 = Here Comes the Pain\n| length9 = 3:56\n\n| title10 = Suede\n| length10 = 3:58\n\n| title11 = Last Hello\n| length11 = 3:58\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline = [[Target Corporation|Target]] bonus tracks<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.target.com/p/melissa-etheridge-the-medicine-show-target-exclusive-cd/-/A-54509879 |title=Melissa Etheridge The Medicine Show (Target Exclusive) (CD) |publisher=Target |accessdate=2019-10-03}}</ref>\n| collapsed = yes\n\n| title12 = A Better Me\n| length12 =\n\n| title13 = Maybe\n| length13 = \n}}\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{album chart|Austria|74|artist=Melissa Etheridge|album=The Medicine Show|rowheader=true|accessdate=October 10, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Flanders|168|artist=Melissa Etheridge|album=The Medicine Show|rowheader=true|accessdate=October 10, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|BillboardCanada|74|artist=Melissa Etheridge|rowheader=true|accessdate=October 10, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Netherlands|85|artist=Melissa Etheridge|album=The Medicine Show|rowheader=true|accessdate=October 10, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Germany4|29|id=378672|artist=Melissa Etheridge|album=The Medicine Show|rowheader=true|accessdate=October 10, 2019}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Switzerland|44|artist=Melissa Etheridge|album=The Medicine Show|rowheader=true|acc